# FlowConformal paper-experiment outputs (CSVs, logs). Reproducible
# via the runner scripts; not tracked. Per the post-NeurIPS cleanup
# refactor (.claude/plans/neurips-cleanup-refactor.md, Phase 18).
# Note: ``ground_truth.csv`` is an INPUT (cached VNN-COMP lookup),
# not an output — kept tracked via explicit negative pattern below.
examples/FlowConformal/experiments/*/outputs/
examples/FlowConformal/experiments/*/*/outputs/
examples/FlowConformal/experiments/outputs/
examples/FlowConformal/paper/tables/outputs/
# Negative carve-outs (force-include ground-truth lookups):
!examples/FlowConformal/experiments/exp1_vnncomp_subset/ground_truth.csv
!examples/FlowConformal/experiments/exp2_prob_scale/ground_truth.csv

# Exp 4 synthetic ONNX networks. Deterministically regeneratable
# (byte-identical SHA256) from ``networks.py``:
#     python -m examples.FlowConformal.experiments.exp4_scaling.networks
# Originally tracked (~117 MB); untracked at Phase 19.
examples/FlowConformal/experiments/exp4_scaling/networks_onnx/

# Compiled VNN-LIB caches produced by external verifiers (αβ-CROWN /
# NeuralSAT). Regenerated on demand from the .vnnlib specs; not tracked.
*.vnnlib.compiled